data.description: Welcome to your dream home in the heart of Spartanburg County's rapidly expanding area! Nestled in the charming community of Boiling Springs, just off Parris Bridge Rd, this stunning one-story home offers a perfect blend of modern comfort and Southern charm. Unwind in the comfort of the primary suite, featuring a spacious layout and a walk-in closet. Additional bedrooms offer versatility for guests, a home office, or a cozy retreat for family member Located in a thriving community with convenient access to shopping, dining, and recreational amenities, this home offers the epitome of suburban living. Don't miss the opportunity to make this your own slice of paradise – schedule your private showing today and experience the beauty and comfort of this exceptional home firsthand. Buyers agent to verify square footage if important to buyers.
